  <brief_title>Suggamadex and Fast-track Cardiac Anesthesia in a Developing Country</brief_title>
  <official_title>Retrospective Chart Review of Fast-track Cardiac Anesthesia Using Suggamadex for Rapid Reversal of Neuromuscular Blockade Following Cardiac Surgery in a Developing Country</official_title>
