  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to retrospectively review our preliminary experience during a
      surgical trip to Tuxtla, Mexico, using suggamadex to reverse neuromuscular blockade following
      CPB and cardiac surgery for repair of CHD in infants and children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
